\****
\ImplementaciónNaturalística-ARegistrarPutuaciones
\Implementación del requerimiento transversal que permite almacenar las puntuaciones de una partida a partir del CU terminar juego
\Autor: José Antonio Juárez Romero
\Version: 05/22
\****
To register the score:
  if the score's level is "Facil", put "C:\AplicacionLudica\Persistencia\easyScores.txt"  into a path.
  if the score's level is "Medio", put "C:\AplicacionLudica\Persistencia\mediumScores.txt"  into the path.
  if the score's level is "Dificil", put "C:\AplicacionLudica\Persistencia\hardScores.txt"  into the path.
  if the path is not in the file system, create the path in the file system.
  read the path into a buffer called original.
  put "T" then " - " then the  score's player then " - " then the score's time into a string called auxiliar.
  write the original then the auxiliar then the crlf string to the path. 
  read the path into the original.
  put "M" then " - " then the  score's player then " - " then the score's movs  into the auxiliar.
  write the original then the auxiliar then the crlf string to the path. 
  If the i/o error is not blank, debug the i/o error.